WEBVTT

00:01.001 --> 00:03.337
[♪ pop music playing]

00:45.254 --> 00:48.966
PERFECT CROWN

00:59.851 --> 01:00.978
THIS IS A WORK OF FICTION

01:01.061 --> 01:02.980
CHILD ACTORS AND ANIMALS
WERE FILMED SAFELY

01:03.981 --> 01:05.983
[♪ tender music plays]

01:18.370 --> 01:20.205
[I-AN] You said you'd let me fly.

01:20.289 --> 01:21.707
Why are you the one flying?

01:23.417 --> 01:25.419
Let's switch. I can hold you.

01:26.169 --> 01:27.671
-Forget it.
-Why not? Come on…

01:27.754 --> 01:29.131
[yelps]

01:29.715 --> 01:31.633
-[grunts]
-[Huiju yelps]

01:31.717 --> 01:32.968
[Huiju pants]

01:35.178 --> 01:37.097
[distorted breath]

01:37.180 --> 01:38.682
[distorted exhale]

01:38.765 --> 01:40.017
[Huiju grunts]

01:42.394 --> 01:43.478
[gasps]

01:46.064 --> 01:48.066
[♪ gentle pop music plays]

01:51.903 --> 01:53.155
Your Royal Highness.

01:53.822 --> 01:55.282
Are you hurt anywhere?

02:02.205 --> 02:03.707
You said I can do whatever I want.

03:18.907 --> 03:23.912
PERFECT CROWN

03:24.496 --> 03:26.039
EPISODE 7

03:28.834 --> 03:29.835
[I-AN clears throat]

03:40.637 --> 03:42.639
-[Youngseon] Your Ladyship!
-[Yeongmun] Your Royal Highness.

03:43.598 --> 03:46.935
Why were you out so late
without the Royal Guard?

03:48.228 --> 03:50.355
Well, we were… You know…

03:50.439 --> 03:53.316
They must have wanted some alone time.
STYLE
::cue()

03:53.400 --> 03:55.026
[Youngseon chuckles]

03:55.110 --> 03:57.112
Did you go somewhere nice?

03:57.195 --> 03:58.613
-No!
-No!

04:02.659 --> 04:03.785
[sighs]

04:04.744 --> 04:06.621
He wanted some fresh air,

04:07.706 --> 04:09.791
so we went for a drive. Beep-beep.

04:10.333 --> 04:12.669
Then you should've let us know!

04:12.752 --> 04:15.714
Aide Choi is a complete mess
because you two weren't reachable.

04:15.797 --> 04:16.798
[clears throat]

04:21.636 --> 04:22.637
Listen.

04:23.764 --> 04:25.056
-You should…
-Pardon?

04:25.140 --> 04:26.975
-What? Huh?
-Yes?

04:31.730 --> 04:33.023
You should get some rest.

04:33.106 --> 04:34.316
[♪ playful music playing]

04:34.399 --> 04:35.692
Aren't you tired?

04:37.110 --> 04:38.445
I am.

04:40.280 --> 04:41.698
Gosh, I'm so tired.

05:00.717 --> 05:02.719
[♪ gentle music plays]

05:07.933 --> 05:09.392
[exclaims quietly]

05:09.476 --> 05:10.560
[sighs]

05:21.363 --> 05:22.906
[muffled exclaiming]

05:25.367 --> 05:26.451
[pants]

05:27.661 --> 05:29.663
I mean, it's no big deal.

05:29.746 --> 05:31.915
We were just caught up in the moment.

05:31.998 --> 05:33.291
I mean, it's not like

05:33.875 --> 05:35.043
I threw myself at him.

05:35.836 --> 05:36.837
Hmm.

05:38.964 --> 05:40.799
[sighs]

05:42.801 --> 05:43.885
[whimpers]

05:44.803 --> 05:46.555
[squeakily] Why did I do that?

06:06.241 --> 06:07.242
[gasps]

06:12.706 --> 06:13.832
[chuckles softly]

06:33.518 --> 06:34.644
It's fine.

06:34.728 --> 06:36.688
You're a grown,
functioning member of society.

06:36.771 --> 06:38.023
[chuckles]

06:38.106 --> 06:39.941
It's not fine at all!

06:40.025 --> 06:42.944
I'm so screwed. What am I going to do now?

06:43.028 --> 06:44.654
[footsteps outside]

06:52.412 --> 06:53.538
[I-AN clears throat]

06:54.664 --> 06:55.665
Seong Huiju.

06:58.126 --> 06:59.169
[whispers] What now?

07:11.306 --> 07:12.307
[chuckles softly]

07:15.894 --> 07:16.895
[chuckles softly]

07:26.404 --> 07:28.031
[sighs]

07:34.537 --> 07:35.955
[heartbeat thumping]

07:36.039 --> 07:37.957
Are you nuts? Why are you racing?

07:38.041 --> 07:39.125
[clicks tongue]

07:41.503 --> 07:42.837
[sighs]
STYLE
::cue()

07:55.183 --> 07:56.184
What are you doing?

07:56.267 --> 07:58.144
[yelps]

07:59.896 --> 08:01.898
[♪ dreamy music playing]

08:19.457 --> 08:20.583
Off to work already?

08:24.212 --> 08:25.046
Oh!

08:25.130 --> 08:27.048
[chuckling] Yes, that's right.

08:27.132 --> 08:29.384
I need to get to work.

08:29.467 --> 08:31.803
I need to work. I'm the CEO.

08:31.886 --> 08:34.764
Need to figure out my successor and all.
This and that.

08:35.598 --> 08:37.100
What a lovely day it is today.

08:37.183 --> 08:38.268
See you.

08:49.195 --> 08:50.405
[chuckles]

08:53.450 --> 08:54.492
[church bell tolls]

08:54.576 --> 08:56.453
[♪ organ music plays]

09:01.166 --> 09:04.878
In the name of the Father,
the Son, and the Holy Spirit,

09:04.961 --> 09:06.087
Amen.

09:06.671 --> 09:07.672
Amen.

09:08.256 --> 09:09.966
[chuckles]

09:10.050 --> 09:11.051
You see,

09:11.926 --> 09:14.679
I'm actually not Catholic. Is that okay?

09:15.555 --> 09:18.058
Well, the man upstairs is a forgiving one.

09:18.641 --> 09:19.642
Please go ahead.

09:19.726 --> 09:21.144
[sighs]

09:21.644 --> 09:23.229
Then, by chance,

09:23.313 --> 09:25.356
do you think I could get an exorcism?

09:25.440 --> 09:26.357
Pardon me?

09:27.734 --> 09:28.735
It's just that…

09:29.486 --> 09:31.529
I feel like I'm possessed right now.

09:36.284 --> 09:37.994
[whimpering]

09:38.078 --> 09:39.329
Oh no!

09:40.497 --> 09:42.916
Could we maybe work something out?

09:42.999 --> 09:45.752
I can make a very generous donation
to the church.

09:46.544 --> 09:47.837
[gasps]

09:49.297 --> 09:50.465
[whimpers]

09:52.050 --> 09:53.051
[Huiju] Seriously?

09:53.551 --> 09:55.095
"Not one to begrudge"?

09:55.178 --> 09:57.097
Yet he just did that.

09:57.597 --> 09:59.099
I even wore white for this.

10:01.643 --> 10:02.560
Seong Huiju?

10:02.644 --> 10:04.104
Oh.

10:04.187 --> 10:05.271
Jeongwoo.

10:05.355 --> 10:06.898
[chuckles softly]

10:06.981 --> 10:08.108
What brings you here?

10:09.275 --> 10:10.276
Oh, a cab.

10:10.360 --> 10:11.986
[chuckles]

10:12.070 --> 10:14.531
That's not what I'm asking.
Why are you here?

10:15.573 --> 10:17.200
I thought you weren't religious.

10:19.077 --> 10:20.120
I know, right?

10:23.456 --> 10:24.833
Wait here. I'll be right out.

10:25.625 --> 10:26.876
No, I can just go

10:27.502 --> 10:28.503
by myself…

10:32.298 --> 10:33.883
[sighs]

10:33.967 --> 10:35.593
[phone buzzing]

10:36.928 --> 10:38.638
PRINCE

10:41.641 --> 10:42.851
[clears throat]

10:43.810 --> 10:45.895
[vocalizes]

10:45.979 --> 10:46.980
Yes, Your Royal Highness.

10:47.063 --> 10:48.523
Are you free?

10:49.649 --> 10:50.650
Right now?

10:50.733 --> 10:53.194
We have something on the calendar
for wedding planning,

10:53.278 --> 10:54.737
but you said you were busy.

10:54.821 --> 10:55.822
I see.

10:56.906 --> 10:57.907
Shall I reschedule it?

10:57.991 --> 10:59.284
No, I have time.

10:59.367 --> 11:01.077
Let's go, Huiju.

11:01.161 --> 11:02.412
That was quick.
STYLE
::cue()

11:06.749 --> 11:09.502
Your Royal Highness, I'll call you later.

11:10.795 --> 11:11.796
See you later.

11:14.257 --> 11:16.926
JUNIOR ALUM

11:17.927 --> 11:19.179
[sighs]

11:19.262 --> 11:20.638
Shall we?

11:24.142 --> 11:25.310
I'm coming.

11:37.197 --> 11:38.698
[Huiju] I told you,
I could've taken a cab.

11:40.074 --> 11:41.701
It's fine. It's on the way anyway.

11:46.497 --> 11:47.749
[chuckles]

11:47.832 --> 11:49.292
Do you like driving too?

11:50.293 --> 11:51.753
-That's random.
-The Grand Prince

11:51.836 --> 11:53.254
smiles when he drives too.

11:53.922 --> 11:55.256
He says it feels like he's flying.

11:55.965 --> 11:57.842
[chuckles]

11:57.926 --> 11:59.928
He can be so childlike sometimes.

12:03.765 --> 12:05.683
[♪ gentle piano plays]

12:08.519 --> 12:09.854
[sighs]

12:12.273 --> 12:15.860
CASTLE BEAUTY

12:15.944 --> 12:17.362
Bye. Thanks for the ride.

12:18.488 --> 12:19.989
-Huiju.
-Yes?

12:21.074 --> 12:22.492
Don't get too attached.

12:23.993 --> 12:25.161
What?

12:25.787 --> 12:27.580
It'll drive up the divorce settlement.

12:28.289 --> 12:29.874
Be it in money, reputation…

12:31.834 --> 12:32.835
or your heart.

12:39.175 --> 12:40.510
[scoffs]

12:40.593 --> 12:42.470
Do you think I'm an idiot?

12:43.471 --> 12:44.931
-[chuckles softly]
-[scoffs]

12:45.014 --> 12:46.015
Bye.

13:00.613 --> 13:01.656
[sighs]

13:07.495 --> 13:08.538
[scoffs]

13:08.621 --> 13:10.290
Who does he take me for?

13:10.790 --> 13:12.959
Someone who can't distinguish
between business and pleasure?

13:13.042 --> 13:14.043
Seriously?

13:14.127 --> 13:15.336
[scoffs]

13:17.505 --> 13:18.506
[Hyejeong] Ms. Seong.

13:18.589 --> 13:21.175
Pull the affiliate numbers
and line them up by revenue.

13:22.260 --> 13:23.261
Throw this out for me.

13:23.344 --> 13:24.345
[door opens]

13:30.268 --> 13:31.602
[Hyejeong] Why, all of a sudden?

13:32.186 --> 13:34.355
They must all be thrilled
that I'm stepping down.

13:34.856 --> 13:37.567
Planning to slack off
without the revenue-obsessed boss

13:37.650 --> 13:38.860
breathing down their necks.

13:39.736 --> 13:41.529
So you want to whip them into shape?

13:41.612 --> 13:42.864
Yes.

13:42.947 --> 13:44.365
[♪ dramatic music plays]

13:44.449 --> 13:47.785
I'll remind them they'll be
royally screwed if revenue drops.

13:51.748 --> 13:53.291
Okay, I'll get to it now.

13:53.374 --> 13:54.834
Have Seong Taeju meet me there.

13:54.917 --> 13:56.294
The Senior Managing Director?

13:59.881 --> 14:02.175
AUSPICIOUS DATES
FOR GRAND PRINCE I-AN'S WEDDING

14:04.052 --> 14:06.512
These are the dates
the Royal Secretariat and the Cabinet

14:06.596 --> 14:08.556
have proposed
for the Grand Prince's nuptials.

14:09.307 --> 14:10.433
All are auspicious days,

14:10.516 --> 14:13.478
so Your Majesty may select
whichever you see fit.

14:18.858 --> 14:21.736
[announcer] Your Majesty,
Grand Prince I-AN has arrived.

14:21.819 --> 14:23.529
Show him in.
STYLE
::cue()

14:31.621 --> 14:32.622
Your Majesty.

14:34.791 --> 14:37.126
I heard you were selecting
the day for my nuptials.

14:38.711 --> 14:40.546
I am considering choosing this date.

14:41.047 --> 14:42.090
Is there a particular reason?

14:42.173 --> 14:44.634
Is it not the earliest day?

14:44.717 --> 14:45.760
[chuckles softly]

14:47.178 --> 14:48.513
May I take a look?

14:49.847 --> 14:52.016
[♪ pensive music plays]

14:59.857 --> 15:01.776
I would prefer this day.

15:03.027 --> 15:04.612
For any particular reason?

15:06.656 --> 15:07.657
We will need…

15:09.742 --> 15:10.827
some time.

15:13.579 --> 15:15.206
I shall choose this date then.

15:18.918 --> 15:21.879
JULY 3RD, LUNAR JUNE 9TH

15:26.592 --> 15:28.344
[Huiju] I'm just here to support the team.

15:28.427 --> 15:30.388
No need to be nervous.

15:31.639 --> 15:35.309
You are our top-performing affiliate
in terms of sales.

15:36.853 --> 15:38.271
The new collection that just launched

15:38.354 --> 15:41.107
is performing well
with the 25-35 demographic.

15:41.691 --> 15:44.694
This necklace is part of
the same set as your earrings today.

15:44.777 --> 15:46.195
Would you like to try it on?

15:46.779 --> 15:47.780
-Sure.
-All right.

15:57.039 --> 15:58.166
Hmm…

15:58.249 --> 15:59.458
[chuckles]

16:00.960 --> 16:03.796
And it'll stay that way, right?

16:04.630 --> 16:05.631
Pardon?

16:05.715 --> 16:07.258
I don't think I'll ever stop

16:08.551 --> 16:09.969
being curious about numbers.

16:13.264 --> 16:15.266
I might be getting married,

16:15.808 --> 16:18.477
but I'll still be keeping an eye
and ear on things.

16:19.645 --> 16:21.731
Of course, ma'am.
We'll continue doing our best.

16:21.814 --> 16:22.940
[chuckles]

16:23.774 --> 16:25.401
Huiju.

16:29.572 --> 16:31.490
Did I ask you to invite that gremlin too?

16:31.574 --> 16:32.867
It wasn't me.

16:32.950 --> 16:34.035
[Dayeong giggles]

16:37.496 --> 16:39.540
I insisted on coming along.

16:39.624 --> 16:41.334
I missed you, you know.

16:41.417 --> 16:43.878
You could've just called
if you had something to say.

16:43.961 --> 16:45.671
Making me come all this way…
[clicks tongue]

16:45.755 --> 16:48.424
Babe, check this out.
This would look perfect on you.

16:49.091 --> 16:51.219
Come on. This new collection is nice.

16:51.302 --> 16:52.511
Try this on.

16:53.596 --> 16:54.555
It's… Whoa, amazing.

16:54.639 --> 16:56.182
This will be the first handover.

16:56.265 --> 16:57.767
What?

16:58.684 --> 17:00.061
My shares.

17:01.771 --> 17:02.772
Right, your shares…

17:04.023 --> 17:05.149
What?

17:05.900 --> 17:06.901
Wait.

17:06.984 --> 17:08.444
[♪ jazz music plays]

17:08.527 --> 17:10.029
You mean it?

17:10.112 --> 17:12.615
You're really going to hand it over
to me? All of Castle Beauty?

17:12.698 --> 17:14.617
-Should I not?
-You should.

17:15.451 --> 17:17.954
Come on. Why would you say such a thing?

17:18.037 --> 17:20.539
-I will kill you if you fail.
-What?

17:20.623 --> 17:22.208
[scoffs]

17:22.291 --> 17:23.918
You heard me.

17:24.001 --> 17:25.670
[mouthing] I will kill you.

17:34.929 --> 17:37.974
Is that brat setting a trap to murder me?

17:38.891 --> 17:39.892
No.

17:40.726 --> 17:41.602
No?

17:41.686 --> 17:43.688
Yeah, definitely not.
STYLE
::cue()

17:49.402 --> 17:50.528
Did you really mean that?

17:51.445 --> 17:52.446
What?

17:52.530 --> 17:55.283
You have other options,
like hiring a non-owner executive.

17:55.366 --> 17:56.659
There's also Director Choi.

17:56.742 --> 17:58.077
It sounds like

17:58.869 --> 18:01.080
you never want me to come back.

18:02.540 --> 18:06.043
-What?
-Father and everyone will finally get it

18:06.127 --> 18:08.337
once Seong Taeju takes over.

18:08.421 --> 18:09.880
"Oh, right.

18:09.964 --> 18:13.175
Seong Huiju is leagues above Seong Taeju.

18:13.884 --> 18:16.262
Thus, the Castle Group successor must be

18:16.345 --> 18:19.390
Seong Huiju and no one else."

18:19.473 --> 18:20.766
I see.

18:20.850 --> 18:22.435
Which affiliate is next?

18:27.940 --> 18:29.483
Since when were they an affiliate?

18:30.735 --> 18:33.988
I was told you confirmed it.
Were they wrong?

18:34.071 --> 18:35.114
When?

18:35.197 --> 18:36.574
-This morning.
-When did I…

18:36.657 --> 18:38.326
-Are you free?
-I have time.

18:38.409 --> 18:39.410
I did that.

18:40.578 --> 18:41.871
I most certainly did.

18:41.954 --> 18:43.164
Seriously?

18:43.247 --> 18:44.248
Let's go.

18:46.667 --> 18:48.085
[sighs]

18:48.169 --> 18:49.295
[whimpers softly]

18:51.714 --> 18:52.715
What the…

18:53.466 --> 18:54.592
You're unbelievable.

19:19.325 --> 19:20.326
How pretty.

19:21.285 --> 19:23.579
This will be your wedding robe,

19:23.663 --> 19:26.248
so please let us know right away
if you feel any discomfort.

19:26.332 --> 19:27.875
-Sure.
-Please take your place.

19:32.088 --> 19:33.339
Ms. Do.

20:20.052 --> 20:21.762
-Can you turn to the right?
-Sure.

20:33.149 --> 20:34.150
[Huiju] Hmm?

20:35.025 --> 20:36.026
Oh!

20:36.110 --> 20:37.486
What's wrong?

20:38.571 --> 20:39.572
Stay still.

20:58.257 --> 20:59.467
[clears throat]

21:01.594 --> 21:03.262
-[Lady Choi] Are you feeling unwell?
-What?

21:03.345 --> 21:04.722
-[Hyejeong] Are you sick?
-Royal Physician!

21:04.805 --> 21:06.098
-What's wrong?
-No, I'm fine.

21:06.182 --> 21:08.100
-Oh!
-What is it?
STYLE
::cue()

21:08.184 --> 21:10.352
No, I'm just feeling
a little hot. That's all.

21:10.436 --> 21:12.563
No, I think you have a fever.

21:12.646 --> 21:14.732
I'm just a little hot. Too many layers.

21:14.815 --> 21:16.609
Her Ladyship is overheated.
Lower the room temperature.

21:16.692 --> 21:17.902
Yes, ma'am.

21:17.985 --> 21:19.570
-Please hurry.
-No, I…

21:19.653 --> 21:21.071
It will be cooler in no time.

21:22.072 --> 21:24.033
Isn't it time for our next appointment?

21:24.116 --> 21:25.159
[Hyeon] Your next appointment?

21:25.242 --> 21:28.037
After this, a royal physician
will come by for a health assessment.

21:28.120 --> 21:30.289
Tomorrow, we have dinner
at Ms. Seong's family home.

21:30.372 --> 21:32.291
What? "Family home"?

21:33.167 --> 21:35.753
As in my family? Why?

21:36.337 --> 21:39.757
It's customary for a future son-in-law
to offer his greetings to his in-laws.

21:43.093 --> 21:44.094
Mmm.

21:44.720 --> 21:47.515
Ah. The chairman's office was notified.

21:47.598 --> 21:49.016
They already confirmed it.

21:49.099 --> 21:50.226
[Hyeon] Thank you.

21:50.309 --> 21:53.437
I'm off to handle the Marriage Proposal
and Wedding Gift Delivery ceremonies.

21:53.938 --> 21:55.648
Marriage Proposal ceremony?

21:56.232 --> 21:59.693
Marriage Proposal
and Wedding Gift Delivery ceremonies?

22:01.111 --> 22:03.239
[♪ ethereal music plays]

22:20.464 --> 22:23.133
"This is a royal edict
for Hyeonguk of the Seong Family.

22:23.759 --> 22:24.802
The King proclaimed…"

22:24.885 --> 22:26.929
"When Heaven and Earth first parted,

22:27.012 --> 22:28.722
human order came into being.

22:28.806 --> 22:32.351
Through the union of husband and wife,
the ancestors and royal line are upheld."

22:42.444 --> 22:44.029
Hand me another piece of paper.

22:44.113 --> 22:45.155
Yes, Your Majesty.

22:51.954 --> 22:53.706
In accordance with tradition,

22:53.789 --> 22:57.167
Chief Attendant Min Jeongwoo
and Deputy Attendant Choi Hyeon

22:57.251 --> 23:00.337
shall observe proper decorum
and carry out the Marriage Proposal.

23:00.421 --> 23:03.382
[Hyeon] "Thus is the royal edict.
Let all be duly informed."

23:25.112 --> 23:27.323
I will now outline the proceedings.

23:27.823 --> 23:29.158
Traditionally, the wedding rites

23:29.241 --> 23:32.077
begin at the bride's home.

23:32.161 --> 23:34.246
However, given the security risks

23:34.330 --> 23:36.707
and His Royal Highness's regency,
they will instead be held

23:36.790 --> 23:38.250
at his private residence.

23:39.126 --> 23:41.420
Then we'll be
at his private residence as well?

23:41.503 --> 23:43.422
Yes, that's right. [chuckles]

23:44.256 --> 23:47.009
And I also have this for you…

23:47.092 --> 23:49.094
Just a moment.

23:50.804 --> 23:54.141
I put together an outline
of the wedding rites, just in case.

23:54.224 --> 23:55.726
[Hyeonguk] Can you

23:55.809 --> 23:57.311
speak a bit faster?

23:59.313 --> 24:02.024
-Pardon?
-I had to postpone two meetings for this.

24:03.025 --> 24:05.110
Yes, sir. Here you go.

24:08.822 --> 24:10.824
FATHER

24:13.202 --> 24:14.244
Ms. Seong.

24:15.037 --> 24:16.038
Hey.

24:16.121 --> 24:17.665
They're all waiting for you.

24:19.917 --> 24:21.210
[Lady Choi] Why have you stepped outside?

24:23.671 --> 24:24.672
Are you still overheated?

24:25.589 --> 24:27.341
No, it's not that.

24:27.424 --> 24:30.386
Then you must return
for your health assessment.
STYLE
::cue()

24:32.012 --> 24:33.055
Okay.

24:35.891 --> 24:37.267
You will have

24:37.351 --> 24:39.520
a more thorough exam
at Royal Seoul Hospital.

24:40.187 --> 24:43.023
Today's examination will assess
constitution and fertility.

24:43.107 --> 24:44.441
Pardon?

24:44.525 --> 24:45.818
Yes?

24:48.404 --> 24:51.740
Mmm… No, it's nothing. Please continue.

24:51.824 --> 24:55.411
[Lady Choi chuckles]
Heirs are precious within the palace.

24:55.494 --> 24:58.872
Once your health is duly confirmed,
arrangements for your union shall--

24:58.956 --> 25:00.207
"Arrangements"?

25:02.001 --> 25:03.877
What sort of arrangements?

25:04.837 --> 25:08.465
The conjugal union symbolizes
the harmony of yin and yang.

25:08.549 --> 25:12.511
Yin must flow to yang,
and yang must incline toward yin.

25:12.594 --> 25:14.388
Once proper comportment facilitates that,

25:14.471 --> 25:16.223
an auspicious day and hour shall be set…

25:16.306 --> 25:18.017
-[physician] Hold on.
-What is it?

25:18.600 --> 25:20.519
Her pulse is elevated.

25:21.103 --> 25:22.104
Uh…

25:22.187 --> 25:23.981
-Are you feeling unwell?
-[chuckles]

25:24.064 --> 25:25.232
Wait, hold on.

25:25.315 --> 25:27.317
Could this be
a post-accident complication?

25:27.401 --> 25:31.030
[chuckling]
No, it's nothing like that. Be quiet.

25:31.113 --> 25:33.365
[Lady Choi]
Then do you have a preexisting condition?

25:33.449 --> 25:36.618
No, not at all.
No preexisting condition. [chuckles]

25:36.702 --> 25:38.037
[I-AN] That is enough.

25:38.120 --> 25:39.830
I wish to speak with her in private.

25:40.622 --> 25:41.623
Give us the room.

25:42.541 --> 25:44.126
[Lady Choi] Yes, Your Royal Highness.

25:50.758 --> 25:51.759
[Huiju clears throat]

25:52.843 --> 25:54.428
[hums]

25:54.511 --> 25:56.430
[Huiju clears throat]

25:56.513 --> 25:57.723
Something bothering you?

25:58.348 --> 25:59.349
What?

26:00.642 --> 26:02.186
You've been acting strangely.

26:02.269 --> 26:03.479
What do you mean?

26:07.232 --> 26:09.193
You're the one
who's been acting strangely.

26:10.152 --> 26:12.738
-Me?
-You're being unnecessarily sweet to me.

26:13.447 --> 26:15.824
While everyone was watching,

26:15.908 --> 26:17.493
you, like, brushed
the hair out of my face.

26:17.576 --> 26:19.244
And your eyes…

26:22.498 --> 26:26.293
You keep looking at me
with those doe eyes.

26:26.376 --> 26:27.753
My eyes have never changed.

26:27.836 --> 26:28.754
That's not true.

26:34.051 --> 26:35.052
Is this about yesterday?

26:40.849 --> 26:41.850
[shrill grunt]

26:42.810 --> 26:44.061
I'm fine.

26:44.728 --> 26:45.896
About what?

26:45.979 --> 26:46.980
About last night.

26:47.898 --> 26:48.899
[chuckles]

26:48.982 --> 26:49.983
I'm fine with it.

26:51.110 --> 26:53.278
It's not like we're kids or anything.

26:53.779 --> 26:55.155
I mean, if the vibe is right…

26:56.156 --> 26:57.533
Why not?

26:58.117 --> 27:00.285
And with the vibe we had going yesterday,

27:00.369 --> 27:02.371
even if it had been a complete stranger,

27:03.163 --> 27:05.457
anyone would've done the same. Yeah…

27:10.546 --> 27:11.588
A complete stranger…

27:13.549 --> 27:14.550
Pardon?

27:14.633 --> 27:15.968
Not for me.

27:16.051 --> 27:17.845
[♪ gentle music plays]

27:19.763 --> 27:20.764
What?

27:22.224 --> 27:23.308
What does that mean?

27:24.393 --> 27:27.229
I didn't do it just because
I was caught up in the moment.

27:30.899 --> 27:31.900
I did it…

27:34.361 --> 27:35.779
because it's you.
STYLE
::cue()

27:50.502 --> 27:52.379
The Grand Prince is perturbed?

27:52.921 --> 27:54.047
Yes, Your Majesty.

27:54.131 --> 27:56.383
Ms. Seong was by earlier in the day.

27:56.884 --> 27:58.719
He has been a bit agitated ever since.

28:02.431 --> 28:05.642
The date has been set,
yet he remains agitated…

28:09.938 --> 28:11.732
I shall go for a walk with him.

28:18.822 --> 28:20.866
Did something happen to upset you?

28:25.829 --> 28:27.372
You appear troubled.

28:29.541 --> 28:32.336
Could you be upset
about what happened yesterday evening?

28:34.212 --> 28:35.297
Of course not.

28:37.007 --> 28:38.008
Then,

28:39.259 --> 28:41.720
did you have an argument with Ms. Seong?

28:44.181 --> 28:45.891
It seems you wish that to be so.

28:49.269 --> 28:51.063
I am merely worried.

28:52.105 --> 28:54.566
You two come from different worlds.

28:55.233 --> 28:57.444
Perfect accord cannot be easily attained.

29:02.407 --> 29:03.408
And you?

29:04.743 --> 29:06.203
Did you attain accord?

29:08.789 --> 29:10.040
[chuckles]

29:10.123 --> 29:11.291
You and my brother

29:12.209 --> 29:14.419
grew up in the same world.

29:18.590 --> 29:19.591
Did you two…

29:21.718 --> 29:22.970
arrive at happiness?

29:27.683 --> 29:29.559
How can I go by myself?

29:31.019 --> 29:32.813
They are expecting both of us.

29:32.896 --> 29:34.231
What would you have me do?

29:37.317 --> 29:38.318
Your Majesty.

29:44.032 --> 29:45.367
[sighs]

29:46.785 --> 29:48.245
Has my brother run off again?

29:53.458 --> 29:54.459
[clicks tongue]

29:54.543 --> 29:55.752
I shall accompany you.

29:57.629 --> 29:59.840
If we say that the Crown Prince is unwell,

30:00.465 --> 30:03.427
they would scarcely consider it
improper that I, the Grand Prince,

30:04.094 --> 30:05.470
accompany you in his stead.

30:08.098 --> 30:10.058
That would only prompt Father
to reprimand you.

30:10.142 --> 30:11.309
[chuckles]

30:11.393 --> 30:13.729
I'm reprimanded every day anyway.

30:15.522 --> 30:16.565
[chuckles]

30:17.315 --> 30:18.483
[chuckles]

30:33.790 --> 30:35.584
Is there any place

30:36.752 --> 30:38.962
for happiness in a royal union?

30:57.147 --> 30:58.148
[I-AN] I did it

30:59.274 --> 31:00.484
because it's you.

31:03.779 --> 31:05.238
[sighs]

31:19.878 --> 31:23.381
PRINCE

31:26.051 --> 31:27.052
No.

31:27.552 --> 31:29.179
So what?

31:29.262 --> 31:30.639
Should we just date a little

31:31.681 --> 31:33.266
since we're going to divorce anyway?

31:36.019 --> 31:37.020
[in English] Nope.
STYLE
::cue()

31:48.949 --> 31:49.991
[sighs]

32:00.544 --> 32:03.004
MARRIAGE CONTRACT

32:05.757 --> 32:08.802
4. DIVORCE WITHIN THREE YEARS
AT THE LATEST

32:26.945 --> 32:28.530
[♪ dramatic music plays]

32:28.613 --> 32:30.782
[screaming, clamoring]

32:32.576 --> 32:33.952
[Im] You must hurry.

32:48.049 --> 32:49.843
[Yun breathing shakily]

32:59.811 --> 33:01.605
[in Korean] Why are you in such a state?

33:06.860 --> 33:08.653
Please get up, Your Majesty.

33:15.452 --> 33:16.453
Your Majesty?

33:24.044 --> 33:25.045
The press

33:26.213 --> 33:29.007
will soon spread the news
of His Majesty's tragedy.

33:30.383 --> 33:33.803
You must secure
the Crown Prince's accession.

33:33.887 --> 33:36.139
His Majesty had abandoned
the Crown Prince.

33:40.602 --> 33:42.520
He wished to depose the Crown Prince…

33:45.982 --> 33:48.443
and abdicate
in favor of Grand Prince I-AN.

33:49.611 --> 33:50.612
What do you mean?

33:50.695 --> 33:53.156
He even drew up a royal edict!

33:53.240 --> 33:55.033
[breathing shakily]

34:02.958 --> 34:04.000
I am certain…

34:07.379 --> 34:09.047
His Majesty will understand me.

34:12.634 --> 34:14.552
This was all for the Crown Prince's sake.

34:17.889 --> 34:18.890
What in the world

34:20.308 --> 34:22.185
have you done?

34:25.063 --> 34:26.064
I…

34:31.778 --> 34:34.030
I burned it all to the ground.

34:50.213 --> 34:51.214
[sighs]

35:14.112 --> 35:15.655
[safe beeps]

35:26.249 --> 35:29.252
[♪ dramatic music plays]
STYLE
::cue()

35:46.603 --> 35:49.189
AS SUCH, I INTEND TO ABDICATE

35:49.272 --> 35:51.941
AND BE SUCCEEDED
BY GRAND PRINCE I-AN

35:52.025 --> 35:54.027
[♪ epic music playing]

36:04.621 --> 36:07.832
"I am most pleased to see you again,
Your Royal Highness." And then…

36:07.916 --> 36:09.626
"It is my great honor."

36:10.502 --> 36:12.128
-Damn it…
-Babe.

36:12.212 --> 36:13.797
Did you not dry your hair?

36:13.880 --> 36:16.675
I tried doing it like His Royal Highness.
Do you not like it?

36:16.758 --> 36:19.636
Why would you copy his style?

36:19.719 --> 36:22.305
Too many feelers? I just thought…

36:22.389 --> 36:25.100
You're so much more handsome than him!

36:25.600 --> 36:27.018
-Really?
-Who does Taeju belong to?

36:27.102 --> 36:29.521
To Dayeong. Ah…

36:30.397 --> 36:32.691
-Stop it. Come on.
-Why isn't Father coming down?

36:32.774 --> 36:34.567
[clears throat, inhales sharply]

36:34.651 --> 36:37.237
But what if Father
does a repeat of yesterday?

36:37.320 --> 36:38.488
He wouldn't.

36:38.571 --> 36:40.240
Father? Father!

36:40.323 --> 36:41.783
I can hear you perfectly fine.

36:41.866 --> 36:43.201
[clears throat]

36:43.284 --> 36:45.036
Father. [chuckles]

36:46.287 --> 36:49.374
You should lighten up a little.
We should be celebrating today.

36:49.457 --> 36:51.209
-[in English] Smile.
-[in Korean] That's right.

36:51.292 --> 36:53.586
You can hate your own kid,
but you shouldn't hate your son-in-law.

36:53.670 --> 36:55.380
Especially, when he's Grand Prince I-AN.

36:55.463 --> 36:56.464
Just look at me.

36:56.548 --> 36:59.926
After falling for Dayeong,
I bow down to her father like it's my job.

37:00.009 --> 37:02.137
Do you see how Grand Prince I-AN
is wasting no time?

37:02.220 --> 37:04.055
He must be beyond smitten
with her too. I swear--

37:04.139 --> 37:05.724
That's enough of that nonsense.

37:11.771 --> 37:12.772
[huffs]

37:30.665 --> 37:33.293
[Hyeon] If I could just have
your attention for a moment.

37:33.376 --> 37:36.796
Once we arrive, there might be a bit
of a crowd waiting to see you two.

37:36.880 --> 37:39.632
Please remember to smile
when you step out.

37:39.716 --> 37:43.011
Ms. Seong, you can just follow
the Grand Prince's lead and wave.

37:49.017 --> 37:50.018
And the Royal Guard?

37:50.101 --> 37:52.687
We should be fine.
We dispatched double the normal amount.

37:53.772 --> 37:54.981
-What about…
-What about…

38:01.237 --> 38:03.198
Do we have an end time?

38:03.281 --> 38:05.909
There's no rush.
You should just enjoy your meal,

38:05.992 --> 38:08.203
but at the minimum,
we're thinking four hours…

38:08.286 --> 38:09.329
Four hours?

38:09.412 --> 38:10.914
[Hyeon] Well, you see,

38:10.997 --> 38:13.541
if you leave too early,
it may be seen as discourteous.

38:13.625 --> 38:17.128
If too late, the other members
of the royal family will grow jealous.

38:17.212 --> 38:20.381
[chuckles] I'd appreciate it if you
kept these things in mind.

38:37.315 --> 38:39.192
Please forgive the delayed greetings.

38:40.527 --> 38:41.528
Father.

38:44.072 --> 38:47.784
[clears throat] Well,
we are very honored to host you,

38:47.867 --> 38:49.661
Your Royal Highness.

38:50.245 --> 38:53.039
My dear younger sister is not perforated.
I mean, not perfect.

38:53.122 --> 38:55.834
We hope she does not prove an impediment.

38:56.584 --> 38:57.710
-And…
-[clears throat]

38:59.712 --> 39:01.214
I, Hyeonguk of the Seong Family,

39:01.840 --> 39:03.842
offer you my greetings,
Your Royal Highness.

39:08.346 --> 39:09.556
This is my son.

39:09.639 --> 39:11.891
I'm the Senior Managing Director
of Castle Group

39:11.975 --> 39:13.726
and his soon-to-be successor…

39:15.061 --> 39:16.104
Yes, right.

39:16.855 --> 39:18.982
I remember, Brother.

39:20.608 --> 39:22.610
[chuckles] Yes, I see.

39:22.694 --> 39:24.487
Uh… [chuckles]

39:24.571 --> 39:25.780
"Brother"? Insane.

39:25.864 --> 39:27.574
You mean, "Your Royal Highness."

39:28.157 --> 39:33.079
[chuckles] Yes, right. He already… Yeah.

39:33.162 --> 39:35.290
[both chuckle]

39:37.375 --> 39:38.376
[sighs]
STYLE
::cue()

39:44.048 --> 39:46.634
I mean, I know it's just an…

39:48.970 --> 39:50.305
just an act and all,

39:50.388 --> 39:52.682
but they're so stiff
around each other, aren't they?

39:52.765 --> 39:54.851
I'm so scared they're going to get caught.

39:54.934 --> 39:56.185
I hear you.

39:56.269 --> 39:59.480
I heard it was super awkward
during the health assessment yesterday.

39:59.564 --> 40:01.983
I mean, can you imagine
how tense she must've been?

40:02.066 --> 40:05.111
To make her heart pound like that?

40:05.194 --> 40:06.237
But…

40:07.447 --> 40:09.574
-Don't you think it's excessive?
-My thoughts exactly.

40:09.657 --> 40:11.868
-Maybe they're falling for each other.
-What?

40:11.951 --> 40:14.787
I mean, they actually look like
they just started dating.

40:16.039 --> 40:17.206
Just started dating…

40:18.249 --> 40:19.459
Oh?

40:19.542 --> 40:21.252
[phone chimes]

40:22.754 --> 40:24.589
[gasps] I need to go.

40:24.672 --> 40:25.840
I'll come with you.

40:26.341 --> 40:28.968
No, you should finish all this first.

40:30.219 --> 40:31.220
I'm off.

40:32.055 --> 40:33.640
Okay. See you later.

40:36.893 --> 40:38.186
[sighs]

40:46.694 --> 40:49.697
[♪ romantic music plays]

41:08.049 --> 41:09.300
[Taeju] Yes, thanks.

41:10.009 --> 41:11.761
[clears throat] Thank you.

41:11.844 --> 41:14.389
I'm actually the CEO
of Castle Hotel as well.

41:14.472 --> 41:17.600
I had some of our chefs come by
to cook this. How is it?

41:17.684 --> 41:19.686
You're not the CEO yet.

41:19.769 --> 41:21.813
That handover hasn't happened yet.

41:21.896 --> 41:23.356
Must you bring that up now?

41:23.898 --> 41:25.900
[stammers] It's almost done.

41:27.193 --> 41:29.070
It's all very good, Brother.

41:29.153 --> 41:30.405
Oh… [chuckles]

41:30.488 --> 41:31.489
Is it?

41:32.031 --> 41:34.117
I'm so glad.

41:34.200 --> 41:39.038
[inhales sharply]
Can I ask when you two started dating?

41:40.164 --> 41:41.165
-Pardon?
-Well, you see,

41:41.249 --> 41:43.793
she used to have terrible taste in men.

41:43.876 --> 41:46.546
What do they call it?
You know, the ones you carry around.

41:46.629 --> 41:48.756
Who cares about that now?

41:48.840 --> 41:50.591
Oh, right. Trophy boys.

41:50.675 --> 41:53.886
She used to be really into trophy boys.
They were always so skinny.

41:53.970 --> 41:56.180
But somehow, she landed
a really solid husband.

41:56.264 --> 41:58.224
-[smacks table]
-Seong…

41:58.850 --> 41:59.851
Dear brother.

42:01.144 --> 42:02.937
Relax. It's a compliment.

42:03.021 --> 42:04.313
Just look at Our Royal Highness.

42:04.397 --> 42:07.442
He's so tall. Almost as tall
as the doorframe. And his shoulders…

42:07.525 --> 42:09.527
Yeah, they're almost
as broad as this table.

42:09.610 --> 42:12.155
-That's a real man for you…
-[chuckles]

42:12.238 --> 42:16.409
He's just trying to say
that you make a really nice couple.

42:16.492 --> 42:17.618
Yeah, that's right.

42:18.244 --> 42:19.579
-Stop drinking.
-Okay.

42:20.747 --> 42:23.041
-Yeah, a nice couple. Mmm…
-[sighs]

42:23.124 --> 42:24.709
[Hyeonguk] Please…

42:25.793 --> 42:27.336
cherish her.

42:31.174 --> 42:33.760
She spent her whole life
thinking highly of herself,

42:33.843 --> 42:34.844
so I had hoped

42:36.304 --> 42:38.264
she'd end up with someone
a bit beneath her.

42:38.347 --> 42:41.434
I cannot help but be concerned
about her marrying into the royal family.

42:41.517 --> 42:44.020
I will do my best to make sure
you have nothing to worry--

42:44.103 --> 42:46.314
If that was all it took,
I would not worry.

42:47.273 --> 42:49.984
[♪ tense music plays]

42:54.405 --> 42:55.406
That place is known

42:56.199 --> 42:58.701
for its troubles and tragedies, is it not?

43:07.293 --> 43:09.337
[chuckles]

43:11.589 --> 43:12.590
That doesn't

43:13.216 --> 43:14.217
quite hold up, does it?

43:16.219 --> 43:17.804
Who are you trying to kid?

43:20.056 --> 43:22.058
Am I wrong? [sighs]

43:22.141 --> 43:24.477
Where was that ever-worried father

43:24.560 --> 43:27.647
when I got into that car accident?

43:29.524 --> 43:31.109
It just doesn't add up, does it?

43:32.735 --> 43:35.530
As you can see, she is still a child.

43:36.864 --> 43:38.533
-She has her shortcomings--
-[smacks table]

43:38.616 --> 43:40.618
That's enough small talk, isn't it?

43:41.327 --> 43:43.121
Don't you have a wedding gift for us?

43:43.830 --> 43:45.540
I mean, when Taeju got married,

43:46.207 --> 43:49.377
you gave Dayeong's family
company shares and even a building.

43:49.460 --> 43:50.670
All on a silver platter.
STYLE
::cue()

43:53.798 --> 43:56.300
[coughs]

43:57.009 --> 43:59.095
Your one and only daughter
is getting married.

44:00.263 --> 44:01.806
Surely, you must have something.

44:03.850 --> 44:04.892
How about

44:05.935 --> 44:07.770
a generous donation to the crown?

44:07.854 --> 44:08.938
[Taeju] Hey.

44:09.522 --> 44:11.440
You're making
His Royal Highness uncomfortable.

44:12.692 --> 44:13.693
[sighs]

44:15.194 --> 44:18.156
You can finish this meal without me.

44:18.239 --> 44:20.116
I thought I could practice restraint…

44:21.117 --> 44:22.618
[sucks teeth, inhales sharply]

44:22.702 --> 44:23.828
…but it's just too hard.

44:33.504 --> 44:34.964
-[sighs]
-[Taeju] Hmm…

44:39.635 --> 44:40.970
Let me check on her.

44:59.113 --> 45:00.198
[sighs]

45:08.623 --> 45:09.624
Seong Huiju.

45:13.127 --> 45:14.128
[sighs]

45:18.424 --> 45:21.260
[Huiju breathing slowly, deeply]

45:35.858 --> 45:37.360
Just let me be for a second.

45:38.194 --> 45:40.821
I'll come back down
once my anger subsides a bit.

45:47.995 --> 45:49.205
[I-AN grunts, sighs]

45:54.001 --> 45:55.002
What?

45:56.879 --> 46:00.007
Are you having second thoughts?
Because my family is such a hot mess?

46:03.928 --> 46:05.221
You must have a bad memory.

46:08.557 --> 46:10.393
If you remembered
what Queen Mother said to me,

46:11.102 --> 46:12.520
there's no way you'd say that.

46:16.941 --> 46:17.942
That's true.

46:21.070 --> 46:23.698
Doesn't it seem like your father likes me?

46:27.285 --> 46:29.120
-You believed that?
-Should I not?

46:29.745 --> 46:32.623
That doting, concerned father bit
is all an act.

46:33.499 --> 46:36.252
The result of him running
the numbers and sizing up

46:37.169 --> 46:38.838
what he could gain by using you.

46:51.183 --> 46:52.184
Who cares?

46:53.352 --> 46:54.437
As long as I'm genuine.

46:55.646 --> 46:58.316
[♪ tender song playing]

46:58.399 --> 47:00.359
I have a great deal that you do not,

47:01.235 --> 47:02.445
and if you ask for it,

47:03.863 --> 47:05.448
I fully intend to provide it.

47:20.713 --> 47:21.714
By chance,

47:23.382 --> 47:25.051
do you have feelings for me?

47:26.761 --> 47:29.138
-All of a sudden?
-Then was I

47:30.222 --> 47:33.142
your first… or something?

47:34.226 --> 47:35.311
What?

47:35.394 --> 47:36.979
I mean… [sucks teeth]

47:38.064 --> 47:41.901
It's true. I can be quite a femme fatale.

47:43.569 --> 47:44.779
But still,

47:46.238 --> 47:48.199
your eyes are sparkling a little too much.

47:55.623 --> 47:56.749
[scoffs]

47:57.375 --> 47:58.626
[laughs]

48:04.590 --> 48:05.716
I do like you.
STYLE
::cue()

48:07.218 --> 48:08.344
And it's my first time.

48:13.474 --> 48:15.267
Restraint always followed desire.

48:17.686 --> 48:18.979
But it's not easy this time.

48:24.443 --> 48:26.654
What? Having second thoughts?

48:28.239 --> 48:29.824
Worried I won't divorce you?

48:32.827 --> 48:33.828
You won't?

48:39.667 --> 48:40.668
Don't worry.

48:41.961 --> 48:43.671
I don't want to keep you bound to me.

48:48.801 --> 48:50.219
You should just accept it all.

48:51.804 --> 48:53.347
Whether it be money, honor,

48:55.057 --> 48:56.142
or my heart…

48:56.225 --> 48:58.144
[♪ song continuing]

49:12.032 --> 49:13.951
I've always had more money than you.

49:15.327 --> 49:16.370
Always?

49:16.454 --> 49:17.872
Always have.

49:17.955 --> 49:19.206
-"Always have"?
-Always will.

49:21.500 --> 49:23.002
[chuckles]

49:39.852 --> 49:41.854
[♪ song continuing]

50:14.094 --> 50:16.055
[phone buzzing]

50:20.392 --> 50:21.769
JEONGWOO

50:25.564 --> 50:26.649
What? Pick it up.

50:32.821 --> 50:34.156
Hey, Jeongwoo.

50:34.949 --> 50:37.785
Yeah, it's over. We're heading back
to the private residence.

50:40.204 --> 50:42.456
Yeah, he's right next to me.

50:43.082 --> 50:44.333
Sure. Hold on.

50:48.837 --> 50:50.881
[Jeongwoo] Your Royal Highness,
did it go well?

50:50.965 --> 50:52.091
Yeah.

50:52.174 --> 50:54.552
My father-in-law loves me.

50:54.635 --> 50:56.303
Really? [chuckles]

50:57.096 --> 50:58.806
I guess you didn't fight
with your father today.

50:58.889 --> 51:01.600
Do you think I just go around
starting fights everywhere?

51:01.684 --> 51:02.935
[Jeongwoo chuckles]

51:03.018 --> 51:04.770
And Taeju? Did he behave?

51:09.608 --> 51:10.609
He was whatever.

51:11.610 --> 51:15.239
I still can't tell if handing over
the reins to him was a good idea.

51:16.907 --> 51:17.950
Yeah. [chuckles]

51:19.868 --> 51:20.953
I know, right?

51:22.329 --> 51:24.373
What about you? Are you done with work?

51:34.508 --> 51:35.968
I'll see you on our wedding day.

51:42.016 --> 51:43.225
I'm sad about leaving too.

51:54.570 --> 51:55.779
[car door opens]

51:59.950 --> 52:01.118
[car door shuts]

52:08.334 --> 52:09.668
[chuckles]
STYLE
::cue()

52:15.341 --> 52:16.508
How did it go?

52:16.592 --> 52:17.801
Did the chairman like him?

52:17.885 --> 52:22.473
-Of course, he did. How could he not?
-Earlier, His Royal Highness was like,

52:22.556 --> 52:23.682
"I'm sad about leaving too."

52:24.850 --> 52:26.727
-He said that before he left.
-[giggling]

52:26.810 --> 52:28.604
Was His Royal Highness nervous?
Did he do well?

52:28.687 --> 52:30.898
Have you been waiting for me
to ask about that?

52:31.565 --> 52:33.400
-Yes.
-They couldn't even eat.

52:33.484 --> 52:34.652
They were all so nervous.

52:34.735 --> 52:36.737
-Still?
-Yes.

52:36.820 --> 52:38.197
[sighs, scoffs]

52:38.280 --> 52:40.240
I know it's late,

52:41.241 --> 52:42.242
but should we grab a bite?

52:42.326 --> 52:44.203
-Yes.
-Yes please!

52:44.286 --> 52:45.746
What about that new place?

52:45.829 --> 52:47.998
You said that place was delicious.

52:48.082 --> 52:50.292
-Where is this place?
-Yeah, we should go there.

52:55.422 --> 52:56.757
[server] Enjoy.

52:56.840 --> 52:59.301
Thank you. All right, then.

52:59.385 --> 53:00.803
Eat up now.

53:00.886 --> 53:02.638
It'll all be

53:03.305 --> 53:04.556
my treat tonight.

53:04.640 --> 53:07.142
-Thank you.
-Thank you so much.

53:09.228 --> 53:10.896
[exclaims]

53:10.979 --> 53:12.314
Mmm!

53:12.398 --> 53:13.899
-It's so good.
-[chuckles]

53:13.982 --> 53:15.859
Your Ladyship, you should have some too.

53:15.943 --> 53:16.944
Poor thing.

53:17.027 --> 53:19.571
You must've been too nervous to eat.

53:21.031 --> 53:23.992
You must be a ball of nerves
with the wedding approaching.

53:24.076 --> 53:28.247
Come on, a lot of people go on diets
before their wedding.

53:28.330 --> 53:29.415
As if.

53:29.498 --> 53:33.293
She's already light as a feather.
Why would she go on a diet?

53:33.377 --> 53:37.172
[groans] I'm taking
a night off from that diet.

53:37.256 --> 53:38.298
-Eat up.
-Excellent.

53:40.718 --> 53:41.719
Mmm…

53:42.428 --> 53:43.429
Mmm!

53:43.512 --> 53:47.474
We've been meaning to throw you
a little bridal shower.

53:47.558 --> 53:49.393
Maybe we can pick up a cake later?

53:49.476 --> 53:52.146
[Yeongmun] Her Ladyship must be tired.
Just eat up.

53:55.190 --> 53:56.567
Areum, why aren't you eating?

53:56.650 --> 53:58.527
I thought you liked this place.

53:58.610 --> 54:01.697
Ah… I'm just taking my time.
You should eat up too.

54:03.782 --> 54:05.200
-Hmm…
-Here, eat this.

54:07.995 --> 54:09.079
It's good.

54:09.997 --> 54:11.999
[♪ dramatic music plays]

54:22.259 --> 54:24.094
This is the Treasury's revised proposal.

54:24.178 --> 54:25.721
Please take a look.

54:27.931 --> 54:29.016
[phone rings]

54:30.851 --> 54:33.353
[assistant] Sir,
His Royal Highness is here for you.

54:35.272 --> 54:36.607
He is?

54:36.690 --> 54:38.275
It's not on your schedule.

54:47.659 --> 54:48.660
You busy?

54:59.463 --> 55:00.547
Can I get you anything?

55:02.591 --> 55:03.800
I like Seong Huiju.

55:07.346 --> 55:08.722
I thought you should know.

55:11.141 --> 55:12.518
[scoffs]

55:15.020 --> 55:16.104
And does my knowing that

55:16.772 --> 55:17.773
change anything?

55:19.024 --> 55:20.067
It'll make sure

55:21.527 --> 55:22.861
you mind your conduct.

55:32.120 --> 55:33.455
[chuckles]

55:35.374 --> 55:37.501
Does Huiju know too?
STYLE
::cue()

55:42.005 --> 55:43.882
I'm talking about myself right now.

55:45.133 --> 55:46.176
Not her.

55:46.718 --> 55:47.970
Don't make…

55:50.180 --> 55:51.640
things difficult for Huiju.

55:52.724 --> 55:53.725
What?

55:53.809 --> 55:55.394
That's not

55:56.770 --> 55:57.980
what she wants from you.

56:14.746 --> 56:15.747
Where's Seong Huiju?

56:15.831 --> 56:18.292
Ah… She went into a board meeting
two hours ago.

56:18.375 --> 56:19.793
She should be done by now.

56:21.295 --> 56:22.671
She's probably in transit now.

56:22.754 --> 56:25.465
She said she was visiting an affiliate
right after the meeting.

56:26.425 --> 56:29.219
-[sighs] She'll have no time to eat.
-Exactly.

56:29.303 --> 56:32.055
Her shares and duties must be transferred
before the wedding.

56:32.139 --> 56:34.266
She has so much on her plate.

56:34.349 --> 56:37.311
Meaning poor Ms. Do
must also be suffering…

56:39.938 --> 56:41.148
Thanks for your hard work.

56:47.362 --> 56:49.323
DON'T FORGET TO EAT…

56:55.746 --> 56:56.747
[chuckles]

56:58.165 --> 56:59.833
She's everywhere.

57:04.379 --> 57:07.007
-Why are they taking that down?
-Pardon?

57:07.090 --> 57:09.134
Oh, that? It needs to be taken down now.

57:09.217 --> 57:11.595
Her Royal Highness cannot engage
in personal promotion.

57:14.389 --> 57:15.474
[sighs]

57:19.936 --> 57:22.522
[I-AN] Don't forget to eat
just because you're busy.

57:22.606 --> 57:25.734
Why'd you pull that ad already?
Make money while you still can.

57:27.402 --> 57:28.862
-[Hyejeong] Ms. Seong.
-What?

57:33.867 --> 57:35.202
-Continue.
-Yes, ma'am.

57:35.827 --> 57:37.663
Next, we are developing plans

57:37.746 --> 57:39.956
for local marketing campaigns
and influencer partnerships,

57:40.040 --> 57:42.626
along with a training program
for the new product launch.

57:42.709 --> 57:45.045
We're in the final review stage
of the contracts.

57:46.046 --> 57:48.215
Okay. Sounds good.

57:48.298 --> 57:49.299
[giggles]

57:50.884 --> 57:53.595
[♪ whimsical music plays]

57:59.309 --> 58:00.310
Your Royal Highness.

58:01.311 --> 58:03.980
The ceremonial robe has arrived
from the Royal Tailor Institution.

58:21.164 --> 58:22.499
Are you that delighted?

58:25.210 --> 58:26.253
No.

58:27.170 --> 58:28.880
[clears throat]

58:28.964 --> 58:30.590
-Where's Huiju?
-Ms. Seong is--

58:30.674 --> 58:31.717
Your Royal Highness.

58:32.384 --> 58:35.512
You must now observe
the proper forms of address.

58:37.264 --> 58:38.265
[clears throat]

58:39.725 --> 58:42.477
Where… is my wife?

58:46.606 --> 58:47.774
What is she doing?

58:57.951 --> 59:01.455
Your Ladyship!
STYLE
::cue()

59:06.585 --> 59:07.586
[Hyejeong] Right.

59:10.589 --> 59:11.590
Okay.

59:11.673 --> 59:14.176
So once you put on
that crimson ceremonial robe…

59:14.259 --> 59:17.596
-Crimson?
-Your eyeliner will smudge.

59:18.764 --> 59:22.017
I finally get to wear red
and walk into the palace?

59:22.100 --> 59:23.810
Here. The Ministry of Rites…

59:23.894 --> 59:25.145
[Dayeong] Huiju!

59:26.104 --> 59:27.355
My goodness.

59:27.856 --> 59:30.859
Why are you here so early?

59:31.735 --> 59:36.406
You and your assistant have little regard
for court or noble etiquette.

59:36.490 --> 59:39.534
As a lady of a noble house,
I'll have to review everything myself.

59:41.119 --> 59:42.120
[sighs]

59:49.836 --> 59:51.713
Mmm… Not bad.

59:54.257 --> 59:57.093
-Have her wedding shoes arrived?
-Yes, they have!

01:00:04.559 --> 01:00:06.269
-My goodness!
-Oh, my!

01:00:06.353 --> 01:00:08.814
[giggles] This is how
you protect your heels.

01:00:08.897 --> 01:00:10.649
You'll be wearing them all day.

01:00:10.732 --> 01:00:12.901
I see. That makes sense.

01:00:13.527 --> 01:00:15.237
-[phone buzzes]
-Hmm?

01:00:18.114 --> 01:00:19.115
Hey, Jeongwoo.

01:00:19.699 --> 01:00:20.951
Are preparations going well?

01:00:21.535 --> 01:00:23.078
You sure you don't want to call it off?

01:00:23.161 --> 01:00:24.162
[scoffs]

01:00:24.246 --> 01:00:26.790
-And if I say I do, would you help me?
-[chuckles]

01:00:30.752 --> 01:00:31.753
Prime Minister Min.

01:00:33.380 --> 01:00:34.381
I'll call you back.

01:00:43.598 --> 01:00:45.433
Are you still not dressed?

01:00:47.310 --> 01:00:49.062
Are you all right?

01:00:51.523 --> 01:00:53.483
Why would I not be?

01:00:56.611 --> 01:00:57.612
Then…

01:00:59.656 --> 01:01:00.824
I shall wait.

01:01:05.579 --> 01:01:08.206
Until the day you can
no longer restrain yourself.

01:01:22.387 --> 01:01:24.556
Do we just wait here?

01:01:25.223 --> 01:01:28.226
[♪ elegant music plays]

01:01:35.859 --> 01:01:37.235
[gasps]

01:01:37.319 --> 01:01:39.237
Huiju looks so pretty.

01:01:40.864 --> 01:01:42.407
No, you're way prettier.

01:01:53.543 --> 01:01:55.670
Congratulations on your nuptials.

01:01:55.754 --> 01:01:57.631
-Congratulations.
-Congratulations.

01:02:05.180 --> 01:02:06.890
[inhales sharply]

01:02:06.973 --> 01:02:10.185
You're officially
the Grand Prince's wife. [giggles]

01:02:10.268 --> 01:02:12.354
So? You like it?

01:02:15.273 --> 01:02:16.358
[sighs]
STYLE
::cue()

01:02:22.697 --> 01:02:24.115
[♪ traditional Korean music plays]

01:02:24.199 --> 01:02:25.784
[officiant] All bow deeply!

01:02:47.055 --> 01:02:48.264
All rise!

01:02:59.484 --> 01:03:01.361
-[grunts]
-[gasps]

01:03:01.444 --> 01:03:02.862
-You're okay.
-Your Ladyship.

01:03:02.946 --> 01:03:03.947
Damn it…

01:03:04.656 --> 01:03:06.074
[chuckles]

01:03:10.328 --> 01:03:14.666
The bride and groom
shall exchange deep bows.

01:03:15.375 --> 01:03:17.627
[♪ light orchestral music playing]

01:03:18.712 --> 01:03:21.047
By sharing this wine,

01:03:21.589 --> 01:03:23.800
you are now equals in status and soul.

01:03:25.385 --> 01:03:29.472
I proclaim to Heaven and Earth
that you are joined as husband and wife.

01:03:32.267 --> 01:03:34.394
[coughs]

01:03:36.146 --> 01:03:37.230
Are you all right?

01:03:37.897 --> 01:03:39.024
[coughs]

01:03:39.107 --> 01:03:40.108
[strained] I'm fine.

01:03:40.692 --> 01:03:41.693
[chuckles]

01:03:42.527 --> 01:03:47.699
The father of the bride
shall now offer words of caution.

01:03:50.285 --> 01:03:52.078
Show caution and reverence.

01:03:52.162 --> 01:03:54.581
From early dawn until late at night,

01:03:54.664 --> 01:03:56.875
let there be no deviation from command.

01:03:58.293 --> 01:03:59.294
Yes.

01:03:59.919 --> 01:04:01.838
I shall carry out your command faithfully.

01:04:03.548 --> 01:04:04.591
Do not look down.

01:04:05.425 --> 01:04:06.468
It makes you look weak.

01:04:29.824 --> 01:04:32.327
-[cheering]
-[♪ marching music plays]

01:05:04.317 --> 01:05:06.152
My goodness! Her Ladyship looks so…

01:05:06.236 --> 01:05:08.863
No, I mean, Her Royal Highness. [giggles]

01:05:08.947 --> 01:05:10.907
Her lips must be on the verge of spasming.

01:05:10.990 --> 01:05:12.450
Just look at that perfect makeup.

01:05:12.534 --> 01:05:14.953
Aren't you glad I used pink coral
instead of coral pink?

01:05:15.036 --> 01:05:16.037
[Youngseon] Totally.

01:05:16.121 --> 01:05:18.540
Just look at that massive crowd.

01:05:18.623 --> 01:05:20.834
I don't think it was that big
for the Queen Mother.

01:05:20.917 --> 01:05:22.210
Definitely not.

01:05:23.169 --> 01:05:26.756
[coughs] Gosh. Why am I tearing up?

01:05:26.840 --> 01:05:29.342
You look like your son's getting married.

01:05:30.802 --> 01:05:33.221
Steward Kim, are you crying?

01:05:33.304 --> 01:05:34.430
[inhales sharply]

01:05:35.014 --> 01:05:36.599
[sighs]

01:05:36.683 --> 01:05:39.394
Our Royal Highness is all grown up now.

01:05:40.436 --> 01:05:42.105
-Hey, we crushed that.
-Gosh.

01:05:42.188 --> 01:05:43.314
We crushed it!

01:05:55.702 --> 01:05:56.828
Smile.

01:05:56.911 --> 01:05:59.831
My jaw is about to snap
from all this smiling.

01:06:01.249 --> 01:06:04.210
How do you do this for every single event?

01:06:05.420 --> 01:06:06.462
Just hang in there.
STYLE
::cue()

01:06:07.964 --> 01:06:08.965
We're almost there.

01:06:25.440 --> 01:06:27.775
THE MARRIAGE PROCESSION OF
GRAND PRINCE I-AN

01:06:27.859 --> 01:06:29.694
AND GRAND PRINCESS SEONG

01:06:29.777 --> 01:06:32.780
[♪ melancholic music plays]

01:06:51.591 --> 01:06:54.010
That is why I told you to veto it.

01:06:56.221 --> 01:06:57.680
What is long suppressed

01:06:59.015 --> 01:07:01.017
tends to erupt
in the most unexpected ways.

01:07:06.773 --> 01:07:08.775
[camera shutters clicking]

01:07:21.246 --> 01:07:22.705
-Congratulations.
-Congratulations.

01:07:22.789 --> 01:07:24.624
-Congratulations.
-Congratulations.

01:07:30.255 --> 01:07:31.965
The most sincere congratulations

01:07:32.048 --> 01:07:34.968
to His Royal Highness
and Her Royal Highness.

01:07:40.848 --> 01:07:42.350
Congratulations on achieving

01:07:42.934 --> 01:07:43.935
nominal status.

01:07:47.939 --> 01:07:48.940
[scoffs]

01:07:51.776 --> 01:07:53.861
[♪ romantic music plays]

01:08:06.708 --> 01:08:08.334
[Court Lady Choi] Your Majesty.

01:08:08.418 --> 01:08:10.753
The Grand Prince
and his wife have arrived.

01:09:19.572 --> 01:09:21.074
[Jeongwoo] Grand Prince I-AN.

01:09:21.657 --> 01:09:24.202
On behalf of the people and the Cabinet,

01:09:24.911 --> 01:09:27.538
I offer my most sincere congratulations
on your union.

01:09:28.664 --> 01:09:30.792
-Congratulations.
-Congratulations.

01:09:31.376 --> 01:09:32.794
Thank you, Prime Minister.

01:09:34.921 --> 01:09:36.255
[sighs]

01:09:37.590 --> 01:09:38.716
[Jeongwoo] Your Royal Highness.

01:09:39.509 --> 01:09:41.260
On behalf of the people and the Cabinet,

01:09:42.011 --> 01:09:43.054
I offer

01:09:43.930 --> 01:09:45.473
my most sincere congratulations…
STYLE
::cue()

01:09:52.188 --> 01:09:53.272
on your union.

01:09:56.317 --> 01:09:57.985
-Congratulations.
-Congratulations.

01:09:58.778 --> 01:10:00.196
Thank… [coughs]

01:10:02.031 --> 01:10:04.033
[coughing]

01:10:06.244 --> 01:10:07.370
Seong Huiju.

01:10:08.037 --> 01:10:09.872
[♪ tense music plays]

01:10:13.918 --> 01:10:14.919
Seong Huiju.

01:10:27.932 --> 01:10:30.476
-[exhales sharply]
-[clamoring]

01:10:31.686 --> 01:10:32.729
Seong Huiju!

01:10:33.479 --> 01:10:34.564
Huiju.

01:10:40.236 --> 01:10:42.447
Huiju. Seong Huiju.

01:10:46.159 --> 01:10:47.493
Seong Huiju!

01:10:56.919 --> 01:10:59.839
PERFECT CROWN

01:11:35.958 --> 01:11:38.294
[Huiju] Toxicity? Me?

01:11:38.377 --> 01:11:39.962
[Jeongwoo] It looks deliberate.

01:11:40.671 --> 01:11:43.049
I knew you would fail to protect her.

01:11:43.132 --> 01:11:44.634
[Huiju] I made a mistake.

01:11:44.717 --> 01:11:46.260
What are you doing? Calm down!

01:11:46.344 --> 01:11:48.638
He's in danger right now!

01:11:48.721 --> 01:11:50.723
[I-AN] Was I being too greedy again?

01:11:52.058 --> 01:11:53.601
You're okay, right?

01:11:53.684 --> 01:11:54.936
I thought you were dying.

01:11:55.603 --> 01:11:56.938
I thought I lost you.

01:11:57.438 --> 01:11:58.940
What are you doing?

01:11:59.023 --> 01:12:01.776
The whole country saw me collapse live.

01:12:01.859 --> 01:12:03.945
I can't be this pretty
when I'm discharged.

01:12:04.779 --> 01:12:06.989
[I-AN] It's our first night
as a married couple.

01:12:07.615 --> 01:12:08.658
Are you ready?

01:12:14.288 --> 01:12:15.832
EPILOGUE

01:12:15.915 --> 01:12:16.916
Don't make…

01:12:19.252 --> 01:12:20.753
things difficult for Huiju.

01:12:21.838 --> 01:12:22.839
What?

01:12:22.922 --> 01:12:24.549
That's not

01:12:25.883 --> 01:12:27.009
what she wants from you.

01:12:37.228 --> 01:12:38.271
[sighs]

01:12:38.896 --> 01:12:40.273
Then why wasn't it you?

01:12:43.776 --> 01:12:45.903
What she aims to gain through marrying me.

01:12:47.280 --> 01:12:48.656
You could provide the same.

01:12:54.954 --> 01:12:56.539
Perhaps I have something

01:12:57.665 --> 01:12:58.708
she wants

01:13:00.293 --> 01:13:01.294
that you don't have?

01:13:15.391 --> 01:13:17.393
Translated by Justin S. Kim

01:13:28.696 --> 01:13:32.408
PERFECT CROWN
